originalText.text: I first met Elana at her ABC Carpet and Home event and later heard her speak on a women's panel at Haven's Kitchen. 'Down to earth' may be an unlikely way to describe a professional intuitive but Elana Kilkenny is just that. She possesses a magical combination of spiritual, soulful, practical, creativity. Clearly a gifted intuitive, her artistic talents are second only to her warm heart. I recently had Elana at my home for a Sacred Space Design consultation and we quickly connected. Guided by intuition, the session felt more like time spent with a good friend. Her suggestions were helpful and reasonable. Her design sense, beautiful and functional. Seeing my home through Elana's eyes left me feeling inspired to achieve the home and life of my dreams! I enthusiastically recommend Elana's services!

originalText.text:
"I sleep like a teenager again thanks to Elana! Elana has a unique and mind-blowing ability to tap into the intuitive world, coupled with very wise and practical coaching.

She uses this valuable combination to guide her clients through stubborn and longstanding roadblocks in their lives. In my experience, the root cause of the road blocks can be totally surprising and spot on. After a two year bout of NOT being able to fall asleep at night, and in a state of despair, I worked with Elana via her Intuitive Counseling offerings.

Her questions, guided by her intuition, were different than what you might expect with a therapist. Elana is guided by her clients' "spirit guides".

Based on my experience, whether a client believes in "spirit guides" or not is irrelevant, as Elana's guidance is so remarkably specific, spot-on and potent. Most importantly, her questions and suggestions are informed by her incredible intuition. She worked with me to gently surface experiences that I was holding on to that I never, ever would have considered to be part of the sleep issue. She asked what I considered to be unusual questions, listened very carefully and made suggestions...gently but assuredly.

Elana always left me feeling incredibly supported, understood and calm. Most incredibly, my sleep issues were resolved. Completely. I still can't believe it!"

Elana has helped me unearth parts of myself I’d closed off long ago, allowing me to become more authentically myself in the process. Elana matches her intuitive gifts with useful practical advice to help you not just imagine your best life but also start actually living it.
